PathFinderDialog

public PathFinderDialog(org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Shell parent,
                        PathFinder pf,
                        boolean showReverse)
Open a dialog to determine the shortest path from one node to another and optionally the reverse path as well. The nodes are obtained from the PathFinder

Parameters:
parent - parent shell for this dialog
pf - Pathfinder with knowledge of the graph
showReverse - boolean indicating whether reverse must be shown
